description: Gets information about an import job started with the StartImport operation.

parameters.name: importId
parameters.description: The identifier of the import job information to return.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name given to the import job.

nested_items.name: mergeStrategy
nested_items.description: The action taken when there was a conflict between an existing resource and a resource in the import file.

nested_items.name: importId
nested_items.description: The identifier for the specific import job.

nested_items.name: importStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the import job. If the status is FAILED, you can get the reason for the failure from the failureReason field.

nested_items.name: failureReason
nested_items.description: A string that describes why an import job failed to complete.

nested_items.name: createdDate
nested_items.description: A timestamp for the date and time that the import job was created.
